headline.print_headline: US Sen. Alexander Fends Off Tea Party in Tenn.
headline.main: US Sen. Alexander Fends Off Tea Party in Tenn.

lead_paragraph: U.S. Sen. Lamar Alexander has defeated his tea party-backed challenger, state Rep. Joe Carr, in Tennessee's Republican primary.
